=== 人權觀察 ===
{{Main|人權觀察}}人權觀察是一個國際非政府組織，专注于調查并公布人權問題，總部設在美國紐約。<ref>{{Cite web|title=人权观察 {{!}} 捍卫世界各地人权 {{!}} Human Rights Watch|url=https://www.hrw.org/zh-hans|access-date=2022-03-29|work=www.hrw.org|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2022-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517132329/https://www.hrw.org/zh-hans}}</ref>

=== 反奴隸制和保護原住民協會 ===
反奴隸制和保護原住民協會（Anti-Slavery International) 是一個專註揭露人權侵犯的國際非政府組織。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Anti-Slavery International - Let's End Modern Slavery Together|url=https://www.antislavery.org/|access-date=2022-03-29|work=Anti-Slavery International|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220518111742/https://www.antislavery.org/}}</ref>

